comments: Carter Jr. (CHI) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Carter Jr. (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Butler (MIA) and does not affect his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Dunn's (CHI) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) steps out of bounds during his dribble on the baseline.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Adebayo (MIA) and does not deliver contact.
LaVine (CHI) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Jones Jr. (MIA) makes contact to LaVine's (CHI) arm during his shot attempt.
Dunn (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Butler (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact with Butler (MIA) as Butler loses his balance when he makes foot to foot contact with Adebayo (MIA) as he sets the screen.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint and actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Nunn (MIA) makes contact to the arm of LaVine (CHI) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dunn (CHI) and does not deliver contact.
Harrison (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Butler (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Herro (MIA) establishes himself in Dunn's (CHI) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.

During the inbound attempt, Satoransky (CHI) calls for a timeout and then inbounds the ball.  Since CHI already called for two timeouts under three minutes, they have none left and a technical foul should have been issues.  (Note the score bug was incorrect in the video.)
Butler (MIA) and LaVine (CHI) engage and disengage as Butler deflects the inbounds pass.
Butler (MIA) makes contact to LaVine's (CHI) arm which affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in LaVine's (CHI) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA) following the pick that does not affect his FOM.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in Butler's (MIA) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Herro (MIA) and Markkanen (CHI) briefly engage and disengage off ball in the post.
Nunn (MIA) establishes himself in Dunn's (CHI) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact with Dunn (CHI) but does not dislodge him from his legal guarding position.
White (CHI) makes marginal hand to body contact with Butler (MIA) during the rebound.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact to Butler (MIA) but does not affect his ability to release the pass.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental contact to the arm of LaVine (CHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Markkanen (CHI) makes marginal contact with Jones Jr. (MIA) during the rebound.
Dunn (CHI) makes clean contact with the ball during Butler's (MIA) drive.
LaVine (CHI) legally contests the shot attempt by Butler (CHI).
Jones Jr. (MIA) makes incidental hand to arm contact with Markkanen (CHI) after Markannen secures the rebound and is calling timeout.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Jones Jr. (MIA) and does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball during LaVine's (CHI) drive.
White (CHI) commits the take foul on Herro (MIA).
